{"tid":1631943,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"10月6號重點煲大","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:46:59.000Z","uid":58490,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"23bd70be1ef596f2687c15fbbe12926bf6f9e255","tid":1631943,"uid":58490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"每次示威都一定發生好多事，打開連登d重點分散，唔知點做好，好有無力感，屌人post仲多過行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n今日拉左好多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />換黎既係我地終於發現大型示威，百萬遊行已經唔適合現時狀況。但不分化不割蓆，唔好再互屌。一開熱門有一半都係互屌鬧前線，我真係灰心左心淡左，佢為我地擋子彈架，仲為左d流血畫面、爛左幾塊玻璃屌佢地？你地有冇良心架<br />\n<br />\n覺得每次示威集中煲大幾件事 唔洗多！要重點！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 極年輕女童被捕！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ip72man/status/1180833846301876224?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fip72man%2Fstatus%2F1180833846301876224%3Fs%3D21&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=fc59fcf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fip72man%2Fstatus%2F1180833846301876224%3Fs%3D21&h=5982f59f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ip72man/status/1180833846301876224?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 的士撞到女手足骨折 膝頭甩骹 不能完全康服 有機會終身殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dalj_k/status/1180786423491776512?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdalj_k%2Fstatus%2F1180786423491776512%3Fs%3D21&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=02d56d28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdalj_k%2Fstatus%2F1180786423491776512%3Fs%3D21&h=54b9ab79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dalj_k/status/1180786423491776512?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫我推，好少開post，但我地放棄，今日百個被捕手足唔會放過我地！！！"},{"pid":"0f402d881e574cd0aeecdfbf83e1d9292ae548d